Puppet module: zone

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages zone software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include zone              # Install and run zone with standard configurations.
include zone::disable     # Disable zone service.
include zone::disableboot # Disable zone service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include zone::absent      # Remove zone package.

DEPENDENCIES:
